Dialogue: 1,0:51:43.66,0:51:45.40,main-jp,,0,0,0,,よう 今日も頼むぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.49,0:51:45.95,main-cn,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:51:45.49,0:51:45.95,main-jp,,0,0,0,,はい
