Dialogue: 1,0:51:46.11,0:51:46.86,main-jp,,0,0,0,,松崎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.04,0:51:52.08,main-cn,,0,0,0,,号外！
Dialogue: 1,0:51:51.04,0:51:52.08,main-jp,,0,0,0,,号外！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.54,0:51:54.75,main-cn,,0,0,0,,拉丁楼周刊的号外！
Dialogue: 1,0:51:52.54,0:51:54.75,main-jp,,0,0,0,,週刊カルチェ 号外だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.63,0:51:57.88,main-cn,,0,0,0,,号外！号外！
Dialogue: 1,0:51:55.63,0:51:57.88,main-jp,,0,0,0,,号外！ 号外！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.52,0:51:59.46,main-cn,,0,0,0,,号外！
Dialogue: 1,0:51:58.52,0:51:59.46,main-jp,,0,0,0,,号外！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.27,0:52:07.55,main-cn,,0,0,0,,下一张 有劳了
Dialogue: 1,0:52:06.27,0:52:07.55,main-jp,,0,0,0,,次 お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.13,0:52:08.81,main-cn,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:52:08.13,0:52:08.81,main-jp,,0,0,0,,はい
